    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeon Misfits</strong>是一款最多支持4名玩家的混乱动作Roguelike游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入<strong>无尽生成的地牢</strong>，充满危险、秘密和超过<strong>80种独特敌人</strong>，每种都需要不同的战术才能生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/bc5b79cf8c1b580acd0f887a53d52ff4.poster.avif?t=1772021876\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/bc5b79cf8c1b580acd0f887a53d52ff4.webm?t=1772021876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用<strong>66件独特物品</strong>武装自己，每件都从<strong>60种强大修饰符</strong>池中滚动其独特的<strong>特性</strong>，确保每个构建都真正个性化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/f1fa1a004919281f851dde46b487a6a3.poster.avif?t=1772021876\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/f1fa1a004919281f851dde46b487a6a3.webm?t=1772021876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自面对深渊，或<strong>在线组队最多4名玩家</strong>，结合截然不同的构建来一起征服地牢...或死在尝试中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/52b6062550a4c98f7e8a59faadbaa4cb.poster.avif?t=1772021876\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320070/extras/52b6062550a4c98f7e8a59faadbaa4cb.webm?t=1772021876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有套路。没有怜悯。只有在永无止境的地牢中的失配者。</p>",
